UID:yAXalOKNYmALl0L-2BIbb
SUMMARY:New ideas conference
DTSTAMP:20260406T030455Z
DTSTART:20260418T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:First Hill (0.5 miles SE)\n\n“Explore art\, philosophy\, and te
	chnology as tools for resistance and optimism” during Night of Ideas\, a p
	rogram that “examines the legacy of the Enlightenment against modern chall
	enges like the climate crisis and the erosion of democratic values.”\n\n S
	at. (5 p.m.) — Keynote address\, visual art\, and panel discussion at Town
	 Hall Seattle.\n Sun. (2 p.m.) — Hands-on art workshops and discussions at
