UID:w2HjvM3ojmBN7d8hI54Iw
SUMMARY:Scott Gibson - Visual Symphony II
DTSTAMP:20260406T030455Z
DTSTART:20260419T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:In March\, Visual Symphony II Scott Gibson invites viewers into
	 a world where music and art collide. Each work is an exploration of the v
	ivid\, sensory experience of sound translating into vibrant\, emotional vi
	suals. As an artist with synesthesia each work expresses Scott’s personal 
	perception of what music looks like. Scott uses resin techniques that he h
	as pioneered and pushes the boundaries of this medium.\n\nhttps://seatoday
	.6amcity.com/events/#/details/scott-gibson-visual-symphony-ii/18280602/202
