SUMMARY:O-Jak Watch Party
DTSTAMP:20260406T030455Z
DTSTART:20260419T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:O-Jak Watch Party is a community gathering hosted by the O-Jak 
	Bridge Art & Dance Festival\, an annual Seattle performing arts festival f
	eaturing artists from diverse cultural and artistic backgrounds. Enjoy net
	working\, food\, a live dance performance\, and a screening of last year’s
	 festival—plus the first reveal of the upcoming 2026 festival theme.\n\nRS
	VP Required: https://partiful.com/e/PzdyRvxfLdFEh3HKYYcJ?c=Ufqt0rhc\n\nhtt
	ps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/o-jak-watch-party/18305788/2026
	-04-19T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/o-jak-watch-party/1830578
	8/2026-04-19T00
LOCATION:Central Cinema\, 1411 21st Ave\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H30M
